(141, 'Kien 1234 đang đi<br><style type=\"text/css\"><!--td {border: 1px solid #ccc;}br {mso-data-placement:same-cell;}--></style><table xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" dir=\"ltr\" border=\"1\" style=\"table-layout: fixed; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; width: 0px; border: none;\"><colgroup><col width=\"382\"></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height:21px;\"><td style=\"overflow: hidden; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; vertical-align: middle; word-wrap: break-word;\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Seung Ri unveils his second teaser full of masculinity &quot;}\">Seung Ri unveils his second teaser full of masculinity </td></tr><tr style=\"height:21px;\"><td style=\"overflow: hidden; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; vertical-align: middle;\"></td></tr><tr style=\"height:21px;\"><td style=\"overflow: hidden; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; vertical-align: middle; word-wrap: break-word;\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;BIG BANG\'s Seung Ri showed his masculine appearance during his solo comeback.&quot;}\">BIG BANG\'s Seung Ri showed his masculine appearance during his solo comeback.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:21px;\"><td style=\"overflow: hidden; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; vertical-align: middle;\"></td></tr><tr style=\"height:21px;\"><td style=\"overflow: hidden; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; vertical-align: middle; word-wrap: break-word;\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;At 9 AM July 12, YG Entertainment announced second teaser poster of the sub tittle song \\&quot;WHERE R U FROM\\&quot; in Seung Ri\'s first full solo album on the official blog. Seung Ri frowned and stared at the camera. Seung Ri\'s sharp gaze showed his manliness, arousing curiousity about the new song\'s concept.&quot;}\">At 9 AM July 12, YG Entertainment announced second teaser poster of the sub tittle song \"WHERE R U FROM\" in Seung Ri\'s first full solo album on the official blog. Seung Ri frowned and stared at the camera. Seung Ri\'s sharp gaze showed his manliness, arousing curiousity about the new song\'s concept.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:21px;\"><td style=\"overflow: hidden; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; vertical-align: middle;\"></td></tr><tr style=\"height:21px;\"><td style=\"overflow: hidden; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; vertical-align: middle; word-wrap: break-word;\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;The lyrics of \\&quot;WHERE R U FROM\\&quot; has the participation of WINNER Song Min Ho supporting for Seung Ri and the beat is produced by both Seung Ri and Future Bounce. This song is a dance party song, bringing everyone refreshing feeling regardless of age, gender with the keyword \\&quot;WHERE R U FROM\\&quot; - the most used words in the world. The song becomes even more special when adding Song Min Ho\'s distinctive music style.&quot;}\">The lyrics of \"WHERE R U FROM\" has the participation of WINNER Song Min Ho supporting for Seung Ri and the beat is produced by both Seung Ri and Future Bounce. This song is a dance party song, bringing everyone refreshing feeling regardless of age, gender with the keyword \"WHERE R U FROM\" - the most used words in the world. The song becomes even more special when adding Song Min Ho\'s distinctive music style.</td></tr><tr style=\"height:21px;\"><td style=\"overflow: hidden; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; vertical-align: middle;\"></td></tr><tr style=\"height:21px;\"><td style=\"overflow: hidden; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; vertical-align: middle; word-wrap: break-word;\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;In particular, Seung Ri decided to shoot the MV for the title song \\&quot;1,2,3!\\&quot; and the song \\&quot;WHERE R U FROM\\&quot;. Normally, only the title song\'s MV will be filmed to attract concentration on this song, but Seung Ri expressed his determination to highlight his opposite and colorful charm through two songs \\&quot;1, 2, 3!\\&quot; and \\&quot;WHERE R U FROM\\&quot;.&quot;}\">In particular, Seung Ri decided to shoot the MV for the title song \"1,2,3!\" and the song \"WHERE R U FROM\". Normally, only the title song\'s MV will be filmed to attract concentration on this song, but Seung Ri expressed his determination to highlight his opposite and colorful charm through two songs \"1, 2, 3!\" and \"WHERE R U FROM\".</td></tr><tr style=\"height:21px;\"><td style=\"overflow: hidden; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; vertical-align: middle;\"></td></tr><tr style=\"height:21px;\"><td style=\"overflow: hidden; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; vertical-align: middle; word-wrap: break-word;\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;The management company said: \\&quot;Seung Ri\'s first full ablbum named \\&quot;THE GREAT SEUNGRI\\&quot; includes a total of 9 songs. Seung Ri participated in writting lyrics for 8 songs. Fans can see the comprehensive music world of \\&quot;solo artist\\&quot; Seung Ri. &quot;}\">The management company said: \"Seung Ri\'s first full ablbum named \"THE GREAT SEUNGRI\" includes a total of 9 songs. Seung Ri participated in writting lyrics for 8 songs. Fans can see the comprehensive music world of \"solo artist\" Seung Ri. </td></tr><tr style=\"height:21px;\"><td style=\"overflow: hidden; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; vertical-align: middle;\"></td></tr><tr style=\"height:21px;\"><td style=\"overflow: hidden; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; vertical-align: middle; word-wrap: break-word;\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Along with the comeback on July 20th, Seung Ri will hold his first concert tour starting with 2 night shows for the first concert named \\&quot;SEUNGRI 2018 1st SOLO TOUR [THE GREAT SEUNGRI] in SEOUL x BC CARD\\&quot; held at Jangchung Arena, located in Seoul at 18:00 August 4th and 5th. &quot;}\">Along with the comeback on July 20th, Seung Ri will hold his first concert tour starting with 2 night shows for the first concert named \"SEUNGRI 2018 1st SOLO TOUR [THE GREAT SEUNGRI] in SEOUL x BC CARD\" held at Jangchung Arena, located in Seoul at 18:00 August 4th and 5th. </td></tr><tr style=\"height:21px;\"><td style=\"overflow: hidden; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; vertical-align: middle;\"></td></tr><tr style=\"height:21px;\"><td style=\"overflow: hidden; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; vertical-align: middle; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system; font-size: 11pt; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Reporter Hwang Jee Young hwang.jeeyoung@jtbc.co.kr&quot;}\">Reporter Hwang Jee Young hwang.jeeyoung@jtbc.co.kr</td></tr><tr style=\"height:21px;\"><td style=\"overflow: hidden; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; vertical-align: bottom;\"></td></tr><tr style=\"height:21px;\"><td style=\"overflow: hidden; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; vertical-align: bottom; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system; font-size: 11pt; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Everything Idol, Everyday Exclusive V TODAY OPEN!&quot;}\">Everything Idol, Everyday Exclusive V TODAY OPEN!</td></tr><tr style=\"height:21px;\"><td style=\"overflow: hidden; padding-right: 3px; padding-left: 3px; vertical-align: bottom; font-family: -apple-system; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration-line: underline; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(30, 207, 255);\" data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;http://vtoday.vlive.tv/home&quot;}\"><a class=\"in-cell-link\" href=\"http://vtoday.vlive.tv/home\" target=\"_blank\">http://vtoday.vlive.tv/home</a></td></tr></tbody></table>', 3, 9, 2, 0, '', 0, 0, '2018-07-12 08:14:42', '2018-07-12 08:14:42', 0),
